/* No global style modifications without team agreement */
/* Use Tailwind classes, avoid custom CSS unless necessary */

/* If custom CSS needed: */
.feature-[yourfeature]-[element] {
  /* Namespace to prevent conflicts */
}
```

## üìù DEVELOPMENT WORKFLOW

### Before Starting Work
1. Pull latest from main
2. Create feature branch
3. Check team board for conflicts
4. Announce in team chat what you're working on

### While Developing
1. Follow the assigned sections
2. Don't modify others' sections without permission
3. Use TypeScript strictly (no any types)
4. Add JSDoc comments for public functions
5. Write tests for your components

### Before Committing
1. Run linter: `npm run lint`
2. Run tests: `npm test`
3. Build check: `npm run build`
4. Self-review changes

### Code Review Checklist
- [ ] Follows naming conventions
- [ ] TypeScript types included
- [ ] No conflicts with other sections
- [ ] Tests included/updated
- [ ] Documentation updated
- [ ] No console.logs
- [ ] Accessibility considered

## ü§ñ AI ASSISTANT INSTRUCTIONS

When generating code for team members:

### Always Include
1. Author comment at top of new files
2. TypeScript interfaces for all props
3. Error boundaries for new sections
4. Loading states
